caption.text:
While having a great hook and structure for your video is crucial, never underestimate the power of visual quality.

I shoot all my videos on my iPhone, and my LUTs make them look like they were captured with professional gear.

Comment “Course” and I’ll send you an exclusive invite to join our private community, where I share my top LUTs. Plus, you’ll get access to a comprehensive 200+ lesson course to help you start, grow, and monetize your Instagram page!

Looking forward to seeing you inside 🖤

caption.text:
Why Content Creators Should Sell Emotions 👇

What sets apart a creator making $1K a day from one who struggles with sales, even when selling the same product?

The successful creator excels by focusing on storytelling.

Their brand and content inspire and connect personally, while the less successful creator focuses only on educational content like ‘Top 10 Tips for X’ or ‘Top 10 Ways to Y.’

Here’s the truth: NO ONE CARES ❌

People want to relate to your story and see you as a real person.

Building this deep connection with your audience is what truly matters.

Your product then becomes a bridge to monetize that connection.

I’ve made the mistake of thinking that only providing value through tips would drive sales.

In reality, incorporating storytelling into my marketing and personal brand has led to a complete turnaround.

My sales have skyrocketed 🚀.

Want to build a powerful personal brand and see similar results? Comment ‘Class,’ and I’ll send you a course on how I grew 500K followers and earned half a million dollars in 15 months.

caption.text:
How to Go Viral with Hashtags ↓

If you have a smaller page, hashtags are crucial. They boost visibility and help you reach more people. 🚀

Here’s a simple 3-part strategy:

1️⃣ Small tags: 10-100k posts

2️⃣ Medium tags: 101-500k posts

3️⃣ Big tags: Over 500k posts

Use these formulas:

Under 1k followers: 10 small, 4 medium, 1 big
1k-10k followers: 10-3-2
10k-50k followers: 7-5-2
Over 50k followers: 5-5-5

👉 DM or comment “Grow” for a free course that will show you how to grow and profit from Instagram.
